How to build PMlib and to install.


1) Procedure of normal compilation

   Edit environmental variables in a make_setting.* file for a target machine. 
   Specify target machine by MACHINE macro in Makefile. Then, 'make'.
   

2) Procedure of compilation from FFVC solver
   
   Edit environmental variables in a FFV/src/FFV/make_setting.* file for a target machine.
   Execute 'make' command at FFV/src/FFV/ directory.


A compiled module will be placed in lib/ directory.
